Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from 'Contrast enhanced' box on Page 03
And I go to Page 06 of Head MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Diffuse' from 'Finding' dropdown menu
And I select 'I describe' or 'I know' radio button

When I select 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'Narrowed sulci' checkbox is enabled
And 'Blurring of white matterâ€“grey matter junction' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perifocal edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Descent of the cerebellar tonsils' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hydrocephalus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Midline shift' checkbox is enabled
And 'Herniation' checkbox is enabled

And 'Cortical thinning' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mesiotemporal sclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cortical tuber' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subependymal nodules' checkbox is enabled
And 'Abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Atrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ventricular herniation' checkbox is enabled

And 'No' radio button is enabled
And 'Weak' radio button is enabled
And 'Significant' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Midline shift' checkbox
Then 'Side' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Midline shift' input field is enabled
When I select 'To the right' from 'Side' dropdown menu
Then the option is selected
When I check the min and max of 'Midline shift' input field
Then min is 1 and max is 99
When I enter 1 in 'Midline shift' input field
Then value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Midline shift' input field
Then value is accepted

When I select 'Herniation' checkbox
Then 'Region' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Subfalcine' from 'Region' dropdown menu
Then the option is selected

When I select 'Cortical thinning' checkbox
Then 'Generalized' radio button is enabled
And 'Regional' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Subependymal nodules' checkbox
Then 'Calcified' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Abscess' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
When I check the min and max of 'Max. diameter' input field
Then min is 1 and max is 99
When I enter 1 in 'Max. diameter' input field
Then value is accepted
When I enter 99 in 'Max. diameter' input field
Then value is accepted

When I select 'Ventricular herniation' checkbox
Then 'Lateral ventricle right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral ventricle left' checkbox is enabled
And '3rd ventricle' checkbox is enabled

When I  select 'Weak' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Central' radio button is enabled
And 'Entire lesion' radio button is enabled
And 'Septal' radio button is enabled

When I  select 'Significant' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Central' radio button is enabled
And 'Entire lesion' radio button is enabled
And 'Septal' radio button is enabled
